As is true of most websites, we gather some information automatically and store it in log files.
The information we automatically collect includes: IP address;
This information may include IP address, device type, unique device identification numbers, browser-type, broad geographic location (e.g. country or city-level location), user ID, browser type and language, Internet service provider (ISP), referring and exit pages, operating system, date/time stamp, clickstream data and other technical information.

